#: ../../M/mandelbug.rst:7
msgid "/man´del·buhg/, n\\."
msgstr "/man´del·buhg/, 名詞"

#: ../../M/mandelbug.rst:9
msgid ""
"[from the Mandelbrot set] A bug whose underlying causes are so complex and "
"obscure as to make its behavior appear chaotic or even non-deterministic. "
"This term implies that the speaker thinks it is a :ref:`Bohr-bug`\\, rather "
"than a :ref:`heisenbug`\\. See also :ref:`schroedinbug`\\."
msgstr ""
"[Mandelbrot集合から]その根本原因が非常に複雑で不明瞭なため、振る舞いがカオス的、あるいは非決定論的にすら見えるバグ。この語は、話し手がそれを\\"
" :ref:`heisenbug`\\ ではなく\\ :ref:`Bohr-bug`\\ だと考えていることを含意する。\\ "
":ref:`schroedinbug`\\ も参照。"
